{"tid":705707,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"近5成狂牛迷想棄用迪基亞","createTime":"2018-06-17T11:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T11:48:57.000Z","uid":4661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2200b402ac82e6d931762ed8ba17a5616cdf91e","tid":705707,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/67/590x/David-de-Gea-975105.jpg?r=1529125265184\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F67%2F590x%2FDavid-de-Gea-975105.jpg%3Fr%3D1529125265184&h=8a428550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=qk5jPCq5806TQkVFI%2BHgWEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=715cf8fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】西班牙《阿斯報》調查所得，有接近一半的受訪球迷，認為狂牛兵團應該把犯錯的門將迪基亞打入冷宮。<br />\n<br />\n門將迪基亞（David de Gea）在世界盃決賽周B組首輪，正選上陣鬥葡萄牙，結果於上半場尾段犯下卡利奧斯式失誤，牛油手把球前鋒基斯坦奴朗拿度的射門拍入網，兩軍最終踢成3:3平手。<br />\n<br />\n迪基亞因為於早前友賽已曾犯錯，自然廣受批評。《阿斯報》為此作出民意調查，發現在39917名受訪者當中，有高達49.8%認為西班牙在周三第2場，應該以畢爾包小將阿列沙巴拿加 （Kepa Arrizabalaga）把關；有38.4%續撐迪基亞，而老將連拿就有11.8%支持。<br />\n<br />\n迪基亞賽後坦然願承擔責任，而隊長中堅沙治奧拉莫斯、新帥希亞路亦齊聲力撐；前者於twitter留言：「最重要不是永遠不失敗，而是永遠不放棄。」後者則表示：「他是我們一分子，我們對他毫無質疑。」"},{"pid":"e01bcbaee2c238862a16409ba0e03533a0a60b50","tid":705707,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"成班反獌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cf8fbd3ca709d52686535b33560a09fca6d2b6","tid":705707,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"用拉爾拿咪仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多笑料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}